des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Portronics products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “Portronics SmartHome” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our “Portronics SmartHome” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “Portronics SmartHome” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “Portronics SmartHome” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Portronics SmartHome” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn on plug.”
“Alexa, turn off plug.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, turn on TV.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
“Alexa, turn on AC.”
